div.p: Step-by-step CPU state changes from real mode to protected mode
CRITICAL DANGER ZONE mov eax, cr0 or eax, 1 mov cr0, eax ; PE bit set

ul.li: But CS still has real-mode format!

li.strong: NEXT INSTRUCTION MUST BE FAR JUMP

div.p: mov ax, 0x10 ; kernel data selector mov ds, ax mov es, ax mov fs, ax mov gs, ax mov ss, ax mov esp, 0x90000
